<plot>The Better Golf Academy's Better Golf For Kids DVD takes children from tee to green in several fun and entertaining steps. Golf Pro and junior golf educator James Pugliese introduces the basics of golf with his unique teaching method especially developed for children. The DVD marks the debut of a new animated character, and features chapter reviews and an engaging quiz to help reinforce the fundamentals of golf.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?543381</url></doc>
